- Use environment variables for configuration and sensitive data management.
- Implement middleware for error handling and request logging.
- Structure your application using MVC or similar patterns for better organization.
- Use async/await for handling asynchronous operations to improve readability.
- Validate user input to prevent security vulnerabilities.